Kristin Bentz, executive director of
PMG Venture Group, says consumers are shopping at dollars stores
and not spending on luxury items. Bentz talked with Bloomberg's 
Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on  Bloomberg Radio 's "Taking Stock" on
July 11th.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 07:29
 